with the city council president

06:30.891 --> 06:32.301
three days a week after school.

06:32.434 --> 06:36.177
The more extracurriculars, the better,
so do something with the other two weekdays.

06:36.313 --> 06:40.352
We need to convey the impression that
you're a reasonably responsible person

06:40.484 --> 06:43.601
