take some drug tests at a lab.

06:46.991 --> 06:49.573
You want me to pee in a cup?

06:49.702 --> 06:51.363
- God.
— Sofia.

06:52.121 --> 06:54.487
I wasn't even using. The stuff was just...

06:56.750 --> 06:59.287
