to say so to the judge.

07:15.102 --> 07:17.138
— Fuck this.
- Sofia!

07:17.271 --> 07:21.389
Toni. Give me a few minutes alone
with your daughter, please?

07:22.610 --> 07:24.601
I'm not a layman, Bob.

07:24.737 --> 07:26.318
I can be helpful here.

07:26.447 --> 07:29.029
| work a very specific pocket
of the courthouse

07:29.158 --> 07:30.739
and that's why you hired me.

07:30.868 --> 07:32.199
