that the problem takes care of itself.

35:59.616 --> 36:01.447
Oh Jesus, Terry.

36:02.995 --> 36:04.735
So much for reform, huh?

36:04.872 --> 36:06.157
(She chuckles)

36:06.290 --> 36:10.078
Is it any wonder that no one in this town
ever gets up on their hind legs?

36:10.210 --> 36:14.453
J‘ In my imagination

36:14.590 --> 36:16.421
J‘ A situation... J‘

36:17.468 --> 36:20.505
J‘ Yeah yeah yeah

36:20.637 --> 36:22.764
J‘ Mr. Big Stuff

36:23.766 --> 36:25.722
