36:29.021 --> 36:32.138
J‘ You're never gonna get my love, oh! J‘

36:41.533 --> 36:43.489
— (Music stops)
— (Mouths)

36:43.619 --> 36:45.530
(Cheering)

36:52.753 --> 36:55.165
