36:59.635 --> 37:00.624
Toni.

37:02.805 --> 37:04.796
I don't know.

37:04.932 --> 37:06.047
If...

37:07.976 --> 37:09.682
I don't think I'm ready.

37:10.813 --> 37:13.475
- OK.
— Sofia, me...

37:14.566 --> 37:16.727
Still pretty raw.

37:16.860 --> 37:19.021
Right. I get it.

37:20.739 --> 37:22.445
But thank you.

37:27.287 --> 37:29.243
(Cheering)

37:33.961 --> 37:35.121
(Applause)

37:35.254 --> 37:37.461
(Whistles, cheering)

37:43.887 --> 37:45.878
(Cheering)

37:54.940 --> 37:57.477
Yo, I'm Kermit Ruffins
and the Barbecue Swingers.

37:57.609 --> 37:59.065
We gonna start our next set

37:59.194 --> 38:01.571
soon as I get back down there
by the Boom Boom Room.

38:01.697 --> 38:02.982
— Y'all ready?
- (Cheering)

38:03.115 --> 38:05.572
— Y'all still got the go—cups?
— (Cheering)

38:05.701 --> 38:07.191
Follow me.

38:08.245 --> 38:10.110
You sure make me smile.

38:10.247 --> 38:12.283
(Man) Wild, man! Let's do it, baby!

38:12.416 --> 38:13.747
(Chattering)

38:21.550 --> 38:23.836
That's one hell of a plan, dude.

38:26.388 --> 38:28.629
(Wanda) There you have it.

38:28.765 --> 38:31.472
Took in four and a half feet of water.

38:31.602 --> 38:34.435
At first I was waiting on the insurance.

38:34.563 --> 38:37.726
That came in, but it wasn't
what it was supposed to be.

38:38.567 --> 38:41.104
And I waited for the government money.

38:41.236 --> 38:43.613
