43:05.667 --> 43:07.703
You two through playing grab—ass?

43:07.836 --> 43:11.169
—(Laughs)
— (Cornell) See ya, Don.

43:11.298 --> 43:15.632
Since we're running up to the city for the gig,
let's stop at Chalmette for some seafood.

43:15.761 --> 43:18.878
