43:19.014 --> 43:22.381
(Laughs) It's a market, not a restaurant, dude.

43:22.517 --> 43:25.509
They got some sit—downs over there
off Paris Road.

43:25.645 --> 43:28.512
Yeah, I know why you wanna drag
my ass up there, man.

43:28.648 --> 43:30.263
Come on, the meal's on me,

43:30.400 --> 43:32.857
or it will be as soon as
you peel off some more bills

43:32.986 --> 43:35.398
