- I can't speak to what your father

48:03.673 --> 48:07.757
was feeling, but maybe he was hurting
like a lot of people around here are hurting.

48:07.886 --> 48:10.878
But what you have to ask is,
are you gonna add to that hurt?

48:11.014 --> 48:12.675
Is that who you are?

48:17.145 --> 48:19.136
(Gulls crying)

48:23.443 --> 48:26.435
Yo, Sonny, fire me up.

48:30.241 --> 48:32.573
(Chuckles) Draggin' my ass up here.

48:33.703 --> 48:35.204
You don't got a prayer, son.

48:35.330 --> 48:38.743
Vietnamese around here stick to themselves,
and you ain't in that club.

48:38.875 --> 48:41.912
(Sonny) Her father? Looks kinda hard.

48:42.045 --> 48:45.629
I seen him around — shrimper who has a boat
here in Chalmette.

48:45.757 --> 48:48.043
Works both seasons, brown and white.

48:48.176 --> 48:51.339
— Does some crabbing too.
— (Bell clanging)

48:56.017 --> 48:57.803
(Cornell) Shit, let's get a beer.

48:57.936 --> 49:01.724
You can rap with your girl after you swallow
some liquid courage.

49:01.856 --> 49:05.189
— (Engine starts)
— (Cornell) Hey, come on, man.

49:09.864 --> 49:11.365
(Cheering)

49:13.159 --> 49:15.901
Thank you! Thank you very much.

49:16.037 --> 49:18.028
And the more observant
among you may note

49:18.164 --> 49:21.782
that I have with me any number of cabbages
thrown at me during the recent festivities.

49:21.918 --> 49:26.161
Along with a couple of carrots
and a spud or two. He caught half a stew.

49:26.297 --> 49:29.539
Indeed, yes, so any of you
wishing to tip a dollar or more,

49:29.676 --> 49:32.008
