— Road Home,

51:20.286 --> 51:23.699
then Not A Word,
then Nagin's Lament.

51:23.831 --> 51:25.537
(Cheering)

51:26.584 --> 51:29.917
What's good, y'all?
What's good, Don B?

51:30.046 --> 51:33.459
— (Crowd chanting) The True, The True!
